paper_abstract: The quaternary Hermitian self-dual [18,9,6](4) codes are classified and used to construct new binary self-dual [54,27,10](2) codes. All self-dual [54,27,10](2) codes obtained have automorphisms of order 3, and six of their weight enumerators have not been previously encountered.
paper_title: New constructions of optimal self-dual binary codes of length 54
